The primary responsibilities of this role, Imaging Scientist Intern, are to:
Analyze Unmanned Arial Vehicle(UAV) imagery data across Bayer’s farms on Maui;
Assist with overlaying imagery data;
Work in overlay imagery data with other geospatial data to build agronomic insights and drive management decisions;
Create or assist in creating data summaries to share with stakeholders;
Curate and catalog imagery files.

